{"tid":1494853,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一位前線巴打,有一個心願想大家幫幫我...","createTime":"2019-08-21T20:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T21:27:29.000Z","uid":306337,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51afb7e63c24b513051e851488898822598cabb2","tid":1494853,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsMJvas.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsMJvas.png&h=ad840fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係想大家幫我推到比周庭sama知道 佢係我呢個微不足到嘅小前線內心嘅支柱！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論我係搭緊車去前線,食完tg返緊屋企,<br />\n我都會開周庭sama嘅ig睇下。<br />\n<br />\n佢嘅笑容令我暫時忘記咗抗爭嘅痛苦,無論係因為tg搞到氣管好痛,定係popo打,見到佢既笑容彷彿就冇咁痛!每當我係前線,一諗到我係為周庭sama而戰,我就充滿勇氣!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每當諗到我受既傷都會令周庭sama離佢既目標更近一步,我就覺得一切都值得！我係周庭sama成為前線嘅！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道我同其他兄弟都係,隨時會俾人拉,隨時會死,所以先趁呢個機會特登開個連登ac,向我既靈魂支柱,我嘅信仰,我嘅希望,周庭大人講出我嘅感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請各位和理非為我呢小小勇武達成呢個心願,推到我嘅女神周庭sama見！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[<span style=\"color: red;\">周庭大人我愛你啊,請問如果我社運之後未死,妳願唔願意同我見一面!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">點都好,記得821七點元朗站!</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港.時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對唔字,禾p牌仔學人開po</span><br />\n<br />\n821返到屋企update<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">今日元朗既手足辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都啱啱撤退完返到屋企</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">推之餘記得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">禮拜六見啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ma0eKEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMa0eKEL.jpg&h=c95f516a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">攞周庭sama嘅新相做update先...</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw終於過100正評啦,雖然唔係咩,但對我呢個開ac5日既p牌小前線嚟講,知道大家唔嫌棄我呢個夢已經好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8043edfcec6cac171c0d4eafa539ae3b227e237f","tid":1494853,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T21:23:14.000Z","msg":"點解我會開咗個新po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要錯晒台,   <br />\n證明我真係唔識用蓮燈,<br />\nsorrrryyyyy"},{"pid":"e61b009a8a85b82ad8cee0380692571621b933f0","tid":1494853,"uid":240455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T21:27:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}